Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371283021052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=374&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=8a80181c4f73c984934953a234e0777a" media="(min-width: 316px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371283021052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=374&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=8a80181c4f73c984934953a234e0777a" media="(min-width: 0px)"><img loading="lazy" class="image_i6zn6lo" src="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371283021052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=638&amp;h=398&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=23b5ddc44a7e1d47591e5d3fcc4f5154" alt="" title="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></picture></div><div class="footer_f1d0ecpb"><figcaption class="caption_c1iimty1">广岛市役所内被原子弹炸毁的樱花（21日上午，广岛市）</figcaption></div></div></figure><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb"> 19日，七国集团首脑在和平纪念公园种植的染井吉野樱花树苗，是从广岛市厅内的“原爆树”嫁接而成的。广岛首脑会议事务局事务局负责人表示，“希望栽种的吉野樱能成为连接和平愿望与未来的象征”。</p><div class="container_c1317zsy container_cly49ce"><h2 class="text_tvah17t text_td9lnz8"> [8:28 a.m.] 日韩首脑会议结束</h2></div><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">首相岸田文雄和韩国总统尹成烈举行了会谈。演讲时间约为 30 分钟。云说，他希望加强两国在经济安全等领域的合作。对于将主持G7首脑会议的安倍首相，他说：“我要赞扬他展现出的高超领导能力。”</p><div class="container_c1317zsy container_cly49ce"><h2 class="text_tvah17t text_td9lnz8"> [上午 8:15 左右] 峰会最后一天早上的媒体中心</h2></div><figure class="center_c1symtaw figure_f1xkd112 figure_fv30jf" data-image-viewer-target="true" data-src-for-image-viewer="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371278021052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=680&amp;h=456&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=67951b2beeb321fe4116cf1d3613716c"><div class="pictureWrapper_p13ffdka" style="max-width:638px"><div style="max-width:638px"><picture class="picture_p169s49k" style="padding-bottom:67.0846394984326%;width:638px"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371278021052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=638&amp;h=427&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=759a4461db7facbdcada479f461c8b7d" media="(min-width: 1232px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371278021052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=638&amp;h=427&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=759a4461db7facbdcada479f461c8b7d" media="(min-width: 992px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371278021052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=402&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=c47cc729b1baea6463dadaf4af92ef6d" media="(min-width: 752px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371278021052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=402&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=c47cc729b1baea6463dadaf4af92ef6d" media="(min-width: 316px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371278021052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=402&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=c47cc729b1baea6463dadaf4af92ef6d" media="(min-width: 0px)"><img loading="lazy" class="image_i6zn6lo" src="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371278021052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=638&amp;h=427&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=759a4461db7facbdcada479f461c8b7d" alt="" title="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></picture></div><div class="footer_f1d0ecpb"><figcaption class="caption_c1iimty1">广岛县立综合体育馆国际媒体中心</figcaption></div></div></figure><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">G7 广岛峰会的最后一天已经开始。记者们开始聚集在广岛县立综合体育馆的国际媒体中心。还是很安静，吃着早饭，看着报纸。</p><div class="container_c1317zsy container_cly49ce"><h2 class="text_tvah17t text_td9lnz8"> [上午7:56] 日韩首脑会议开始</h2></div><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">日本首相岸田文雄与韩国总统尹成烈的首脑会谈已经开始。这将是两国领导人自 3 月以来首次在日本会面。</p><div class="container_c1317zsy container_cly49ce"><h2 class="text_tvah17t text_td9lnz8"> [上午7:35] 日韩领导人为韩国原子弹爆炸受害者祈祷，参观纪念碑并献花</h2></div><figure class="center_c1symtaw figure_f1xkd112 figure_fv30jf" data-image-viewer-target="true" data-src-for-image-viewer="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371300021052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=680&amp;h=425&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=76cd9b12c30186583b8370f40db8a06f"><div class="pictureWrapper_p13ffdka" style="max-width:638px"><div style="max-width:638px"><picture class="picture_p169s49k" style="padding-bottom:62.539184952978054%;width:638px"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371300021052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=638&amp;h=399&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=c84c362aff5a2965f6c8245527922dc4" media="(min-width: 1232px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371300021052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=638&amp;h=399&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=c84c362aff5a2965f6c8245527922dc4" media="(min-width: 992px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371300021052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=375&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=d420a4da8c61bb6d540bed0109902c55" media="(min-width: 752px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371300021052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=375&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=d420a4da8c61bb6d540bed0109902c55" media="(min-width: 316px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2