7%;width:638px"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371223021052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=638&amp;h=424&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=1b13c4cd5029a7218bd3b1dd3ac3fd08" media="(min-width: 1232px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371223021052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=638&amp;h=424&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=1b13c4cd5029a7218bd3b1dd3ac3fd08" media="(min-width: 992px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371223021052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=398&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=4b29155940b687f60431d39b7f0bb698" media="(min-width: 752px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371223021052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=398&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=4b29155940b687f60431d39b7f0bb698" media="(min-width: 316px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371223021052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=398&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=4b29155940b687f60431d39b7f0bb698" media="(min-width: 0px)"><img loading="lazy" class="image_i6zn6lo" src="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371223021052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=638&amp;h=424&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=1b13c4cd5029a7218bd3b1dd3ac3fd08" alt="" title="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></picture></div><div class="footer_f1d0ecpb"><figcaption class="caption_c1iimty1">警察准备限制和平纪念公园周围的交通（21日上午，广岛市中区） </figcaption></div></div></figure><div class="container_c1317zsy container_cly49ce"><h2 class="text_tvah17t text_td9lnz8"> 【第20期文摘】泽连斯基访日并与英法德意印四国领导人举行会谈</h2></div><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">20日，G7峰会的第二天，与新兴和发展中国家的关系和经济安全成为议程。下午，韩国、印度、澳大利亚等受邀国进行了会谈。主席国日本没有等到最后一天就发表了首脑会议宣言。</p><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">泽伦斯基总统乘坐法国政府专机抵达广岛机场，面对面出席峰会。我参加了与印度、英国、法国、德国和意大利等国家领导人的会晤。</p><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">当天晚上还举行了日本、美国、澳大利亚和印度领导人的“四方”首脑会议。虽然原定于峰会结束后在澳大利亚举行，但美国总统拜登取消了原计划的澳大利亚访问。</p><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">在国际媒体中心举办了一场宣传广岛美食的活动。</p><div class="container_ci59o1r"><p class="title_t1guwbqo"> 【第20条时间线】</p><ul class="list_l1av0zdp"><li class="overrideStyle_oe0851q"> <a href="https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXZQOUA153A90V10C23A5000000" data-track-article-link="true">G7广岛峰会20日动向 泽连斯基先生来日后</a></li></ul></div><div class="container_c1317zsy container_cly49ce"><h2 class="text_tvah17t text_td9lnz8"> [第20次茶歇菜单] Momiji馒头和金融家排队</h2></div><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">在峰会的第二天，我们还为领导人提供了喝咖啡休息的机会。继19日的第一天之后，广岛著名的枫糖馒头和柠檬金融家等甜点被列为茶点。 </p><figure class="center_c1symtaw figure_f1xkd112 figure_fv30jf" data-image-viewer-target="true" data-src-for-image-viewer="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371192020052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=680&amp;h=536&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=4d6453101d6dc84211bc6c78c77ea0c6"><div class="pictureWrapper_p13ffdka" style="max-width:425px"><div style="max-width:425px"><picture class="picture_p169s49k" style="padding-bottom:78.82352941176471%;width:425px"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371192020052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=425&amp;h=334&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=416ae7cd021108bb61f4a4f2ae115655" media="(min-width: 1232px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3371192020052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=425&amp;h=334&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=416ae7cd021108bb61f4a4f2ae115655" media="(min-width: 992px)"><source srcset="https://article-